An '''empath''' was a [[Sentience/Legends|sentient]] who apparently had the ability to manipulate the minds of [[Human/Legends|Humans]], and possibly other species as well. They could reach into their victim's minds and paralyze them, or draw out the buried memories of their past misdeeds, overwhelming them with their own conscience. In this way the empath's suggestion for their absolution, that they commit [[Death/Legends|suicide]], was accepted and embraced.

The only recorded empath was [[Clat]] of the [[Guild of Vindicators]].

